  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My sisters [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jolan, Berta, Izabella, and Regina, and Helen were all living at home in, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the time of the, of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of them, when the Holocaust set in, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they were all [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] really like each other, all-- but at the same time, of course, all different personalities and all of them striving to make themselves into the image of my mother, just like I did.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister Jolan was the eldest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we called her in the family [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sisters were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kind of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] elegant young women in, in town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were kind of fashionable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were-- the whole family was a rather well-respected and well-known family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, they, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they, too, were looked up to by their peers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in their case, too, as has been the case in my particular case, we had a certain following.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were almost all Pied Pipers in that sense.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We, we all had the coterie of friends who, who sort of looked upon us as the trendsetters and the pacesetters.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It, it wasn't only that we were friends, but we, we somehow-- we were, as I say, trendsetters for, for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jolan, as I have told you, J-O-L-A-N.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was the oldest, or is it the eldest?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then came Berta, B-E-R-T-A, who the nickname was Csicsa [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That is spelled C-S-I-C-S-A and means big mouth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She, she was and is a big mouth.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
